    "description": "<strong>《咩顶之灾》</strong>是一款每关只花5分钟的回合制策略游戏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236280/extras/980833886e7878dfbf4ede9c81bae6fe.poster.avif?t=1743081645\" width=616 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236280/extras/980833886e7878dfbf4ede9c81bae6fe.webm?t=1743081645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236280/extras/980833886e7878dfbf4ede9c81bae6fe.mp4?t=1743081645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在迷雾中寻找资源，将散装城市连接成坚不可摧的网络，制作具备特殊能力的强力卡牌。回合耗尽，恶魔大军便会无情入侵，不知你亲手打造的防线能否经受住考验？只要有一座城市屹立不倒，就算大获全胜。一旦失败，青青草原便会化作炼狱。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 短平快 - 在地图中自由探索，不断拓展城市圈，开采水晶矿，打造抵御恶魔的防线。每关只需5分钟，午休都能见缝插针玩。<br></li><li> 易上手 - 本作的游戏设计并不复杂，上手容易精通难。<br></li><li> 轻压力 - 专注于探索与成长。关卡结束时，恶魔才会开始大举进攻。你可以边嚼爆米花边关注战局。<br></li><li> 自定策略 - 卡牌池规模超过100张，从中挑选出心仪的牌组；更有40余名向导可选择，足够你募集到一队人马。如此一来，便可以做到局局不一样。<br></li><li> 重复可玩 - 恶魔各有特色，迷你挑战也关关不同，每局都独一无二。<br></li><li> 凶险又迷人 - 这里满是萌萌小羊和魔法小屋。只要不大啖羊排，连恶魔也称得上可爱……</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236280/extras/f701ecf942be53048846bb3c1227a674.poster.avif?t=1743081645\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236280/extras/f701ecf942be53048846bb3c1227a674.webm?t=1743081645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236280/extras/f701ecf942be53048846bb3c1227a674.mp4?t=1743081645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
